{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c55132a894","title":"给王中的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"baf8f5d8a8","index":0,"year":1943,"month":1,"day":10,"articleId":"c55132a894"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji17","name":"毛泽东全集第17卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji17.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji17":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b8f1805b00","type":"paragraph","text":"给王中的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"c55132a894"},{"id":"6cb1ac5ee7","type":"paragraph","text":"（1943年1月10日）王中同志：你送来的材料很有用。这是小集体生产与个人生产，我还要整个敌工委的“一九四二年的生产总结与一九四三年的生产计划”以便看出全股情形，请通知有关同志在十大内外做好交我。做这个总结与计划时，应包括（一）全机关生产，（二）小集体生产，（三）个人生产，当然主要的是全机关生产。其中要指出成绩，又要指出缺点，要有自我批评敬礼！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"c55132a894"},{"id":"682e429675","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"c55132a894"},{"id":"24c5450ee2","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十日你的意见，希望以后对我谈一下[11王中（1906-1981），浙江余姚人，当时在中共中央敌区工作委员会负责行致管理工作。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"c55132a894"}],"page":{"id":"d256870603","publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"c55132a894","start":483,"end":483}}}},"__N_SSG":true}